                {
                  "subject": "Quick CTF question for {{firstName}} ",
                  "body": "<div>Hi {{FirstName}},</div><div><br /></div><div>I was looking at {{companyName}} and noticed you’re organizing CTFs regularly.</div><div><br /></div><div>Quick question, how much time do you usually lose *before* the CTF even starts?</div><div>Infra setup, DevOps, testing, last-minute fixes, etc.</div><div><br /></div><div>We built a CTF hosting platform specifically to remove that entire layer.</div><div><br /></div><div>Instead of pitching anything, I wanted to share two free resources we give organizers:</div><div><br /></div><div>1) A free trial (spin up a full CTF environment without DevOps)</div><div>2) A short CTF Planning &amp; Execution Guide covering:</div><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;--darkreader-inline-color:var(--darkreader-text-000000, #f0ebe2);--darkreader-inline-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>Pre-CTF Planning</div></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;--darkreader-inline-color:var(--darkreader-text-000000, #f0ebe2);--darkreader-inline-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>CTF Day Execution</div></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;--darkreader-inline-color:var(--darkreader-text-000000, #f0ebe2);--darkreader-inline-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>Post-CTF Wrap-Up</div></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;--darkreader-inline-color:var(--darkreader-text-000000, #f0ebe2);--darkreader-inline-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>Planning Checklist</div></li></ul><div><br /></div><div>Happy to send both if useful.</div><div><br />Reply “Send” and I’ll send them over.<br /><br />Sincerely,<br />Noah</div>"
                }
              ],
              "delay_unit": "days",
              "pre_delay_unit": "days"
            },
