              "variants": [
                {
                  "subject": "Re: {{companyName}} ",
                  "body": "<div>{{FirstName}}, quick follow-up.</div><div><br /></div><div>Not sure if reducing CTF prep time is a priority right now.</div><div><br /></div><div>If it is, I can share:</div><div>• free trial access</div><div>• the CTF Planning &amp; Execution Guide</div><div><br /></div><div>If not, no worries at all.</div><div>Reply “Send” and I’ll send them over.</div><div><br />Sincerely,<br />Noah</div><div><br /></div>"
